videos.description: SMU's Sterling Brown connects on a 3-pointer to put SMU ahead 29-8.
videos.headline: SMU takes 21-point lead on Brown 3-pointer

videos.description: Three quick turnovers give Memphis's Markel Crawford  a wide-open dunk.
videos.headline: Crazy sequence leads to Memphis dunk

videos.description: SMU's Shake Milton assists on two alley-oop dunks to Ben Moore and Jarrey Foster.
videos.headline: SMU scores with a pair of alley-oop slams

videos.description: SMU's Shake Milton gets a steal and assists on a Sterling Brown one-handed slam at the other end.
videos.headline: Brown makes Memphis pay with a powerful one-handed dunk

videos.description: SMU's Jarrey Foster gives SMU 100 points for the game with a put-back slam.
videos.headline: Foster caps off SMU win with put-back dunk

videos.description: SMU head coach Tim Jankovich's thoughts on winning the American conference regular season title.
videos.headline: Tim Jankovich on how it feels to win regular season conference title
